issue.title: Support direct comparisons of byte[] to avoid copy

rename.from: Add methods to direct comparisons between byte[] and Bytes
rename.to: Support direct comparisons between byte[] and Bytes

body: If interested in implementing this take a a look at [compareTo(Bytes)](https://github.com/apache/fluo/blob/rel/fluo-1.1.0-incubating/modules/api/src/main/java/org/apache/fluo/api/data/Bytes.java#L199) and [equals(Object)](https://github.com/apache/fluo/blob/rel/fluo-1.1.0-incubating/modules/api/src/main/java/org/apache/fluo/api/data/Bytes.java#L222).  Maybe all of these methods could be refactored to share code, not sure.  Also unit test will need to be added to [BytesTest](https://github.com/apache/fluo/blob/rel/fluo-1.1.0-incubating/modules/api/src/test/java/org/apache/fluo/api/data/BytesTest.java)
